  "None suggested yet": "Nessun suggerimento",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Dopo la risposta, una chiamata silenziosa genera il JSON. ~250–300s/messaggio.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Una chiamata API — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Nessun cambio profilo — nessun rischio",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ L'IA ha il contesto completo",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× più veloce di Separato",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Usa token dal budget principale (~1.700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Può ridurre leggermente la narrativa",
  "✓ Clean responses — narrative never token-competes with tracker": "✓ Risposte pulite — nessuna competizione",
  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ Budget dedicato per il tracker",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Può usare un profilo/preset diverso",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Due chiamate API — 2–3× più lento",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s di attesa tra le chiamate",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ a 8 msg — riduci a 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Il cambio profilo può causare cancellazione",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Include snapshot precedente (~1.9K) se non = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Quanti messaggi recenti includere.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Solo Separata — Insieme usa il contesto ST.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Più veloce. Per scene 1 a 1 (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Bilanciato. Per la maggior parte (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Migliore continuità per scene complesse (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Massimo contesto ma più lento e costoso",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Fattore principale. A 8 msg ~10K — raddoppiare raddoppia il tempo. 3–4 riduce 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Solo modalità Separata.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Tentativi se il JSON è invalido.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Per JSON su GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Incorpora snapshot nel contesto. Solo Separata. Il tracker riceve sempre il precedente.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Ogni snapshot +~1.9K. 0 per eliminare. 1 per continuità. Sopra 1 raramente utile.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Iniettato come contesto invisibile — info autorevole.",
  "Appears as if the user said it — some models respond more attentively.": "Appare come detto dall'utente — alcuni modelli rispondono meglio.",
  "Appears as previous AI output — can reinforce the AI's own memory but may confuse some models.": "Come output precedente — può rinforzare la memoria ma confondere.",
  "Separate generation runs an isolated API call — it needs lorebook context injected since ST won't provide it automatically.": "Generazione separata è chiamata isolata — serve lorebook.",
  "Together mode uses the normal generation — ST already injects lorebooks into context, so including them here would be redundant.": "Insieme usa generazione normale — ST già inietta lorebook.",
